author: Dominic Chopping
description: Swedish prosecutors said they have decided to discontinue a probe into alleged rape targeting WikiLeaks founder Julian Assange.
title: Sweden Ends Probe Against WikiLeaks Founder Julian Assange

author: By Julian Robinson
description: The decision to drop the investigation into WikiLeaks founder Julian Assange was announced by Sweden's Director of Public Prosecution, Marianne Ny.
title: BREAKING NEWS: Sweden drops its prosecution against Julian Assange

author: Matthew Hughes
description: Sweden's Director of Public Prosecutions has announced it has dropped the investigation into Julian Assange's rape charges, which have dogged the Australian-born Wikileaks founder since ...
title: Sweden just dropped the Julian Assange rape investigation

description: Sweden's top prosecutor has said she has dropped a rape investigation into Julian Assange, the founder of WikiLeaks.
title: Julian Assange 'to seek asylum in Franbce' after rape investigation dropped by Swedish prosecutors

author: Lizzie Dearden
description: Julian Assange will be arrested if he leaves the Ecuadorian embassy despite Sweden dropping its sexual assault investigation, British police have confirmed. A spokesperson for the Metropolitan Police said that despite Sweden's European arrest warrant for the WikiLeaks founder being lifted, he was under a separate warrant for skipping bail.
title: Julian Assange will still be arrested if he leaves Ecuadorian embassy

description: Swedish prosecutors end investigations into rape allegations against WikiLeaks founder Julian Assange after a seven-year legal battle.
title: Swedish prosecutors drop Assange rape investigation

author: CNBC
description: Swedish prosecutors said they would drop a preliminary investigation into an allegation of rape against WikiLeaks founder Julian Assange.
title: Sweden drops Assange investigation, UK police says he still faces arrest

author: Alle Beiträge von dpa  anzeigen.
description: Zu 35 Jahren Haft wurde Chelsea Manning im Jahr 2010 verurteilt – wegen Geheimnisverrat. Jetzt ist die Whistleblowerin wieder auf freiem Fuß. Auch Julian Assange schöpft wieder Hoffnung.
title: Whistleblowerin entlassen: Chelsea Manning ist frei

author: Spiegel Online
description: Die Ermittlungen gegen Julian Assange wegen des Vorwurfs einer Sexualstraftat in Schweden werden eingestellt. Ecuadors Botschaft in London wird der WikiLeaks-Gründer wohl trotzdem nicht verlassen.
title: WikiLeaks-Gründer: Schweden stellt Ermittlungen gegen Assange ein

author: Jeremy Hodges, Jonas O Bergman
description: WikiLeaks founder Julian Assange moved closer to freedom Friday after Swedish prosecutors moved to drop a rape investigation against him, leaving the door open for him to emerge from his self-imposed exile in a London embassy.
title: WikiLeaks's Assange Closer to Freedom as Swedes Drop Rape Case
